videos.description: Jared Butler dribbles around, finds his spot and drills a pull-up 3-pointer for the Baylor Bears.

videos.description: Oklahoma State head coach Mike Boynton is ejected for his conduct after a call then shows his sportsmanship by shaking the hands of the Baylor basketball team before exiting.
